### **9. `package.json` (Root Directory)**
Dependencies for the entire project.

```json
{
  "name": "decentralized-credit-scoring",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "A decentralized credit scoring system",
  "scripts": {
    "deploy": "npx hardhat run scripts/deploy.js --network rinkeby"
  },
  "dependencies": {
    "@nomiclabs/hardhat-ethers": "^2.0.6",
    "ethers": "^5.7.2",
